TABLE.name: I/345/transits
TABLE.DESCRIPTION: Calibrated FoV transit photometry for CU5, consolidated and provided by CU7 for variable stars in Gaia DR2 (epoch_photometry, part 2)

FIELD.name: recno
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Record number assigned by the VizieR team. Should Not be used for identification.

FIELD.name: Source
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Source Identifier (source_id) (G2)

FIELD.name: TransitID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Transit Identifier as defined in JP-011 and received by DPCI from IDT (transit_id)

FIELD.name: TimeG
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Transit averaged G band observation time (JD-2455197.5) (g_transit_time) (1)

FIELD.name: FG
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Transit averaged G band flux (g_transit_flux) (2)

FIELD.name: e_FG
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Error on the transit averaged G band flux (g_transit_flux_error)

FIELD.name: Gmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Transit averaged G band magnitude (converted from transit averaged G band flux) (g_transit_mag)

FIELD.name: e_Gmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Error on transit averaged G band magnitude, added by CDS (g_transit_mag_error)

FIELD.name: TimeBP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? BP CCD transit observation time (JD-2455197.5) (bp_obs_time) (1)

FIELD.name: FBP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? BP band flux (bp_flux)

FIELD.name: e_FBP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Error on the BP band flux (bp_flux_error)

FIELD.name: BPmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? BP band magnitude (converted from BP band flux) (bp_mag)

FIELD.name: e_BPmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Error on the BP band magnitude, added by CDS (bp_mag_error)

FIELD.name: TimeRP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? RP CCD transit observation time (JD-2455197.5) (rp_obs_time) (1)

FIELD.name: FRP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? RP band flux (rp_flux)

FIELD.name: e_FRP
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Error on the RP band flux (rp_flux_error)

FIELD.name: RPmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? RP band magnitude (converted from RP band flux) (rp_mag)

FIELD.name: e_RPmag
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: ? Error on the RP band magnitude, added by CDS (rp_mag_error)

FIELD.name: VarGr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: [0/1]? Average G transit photometry rejected by variability processing (variability_flag_g_reject) (3) [NULL integer written as an empty string]

FIELD.name: VarBPr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: [0/1]? Average BP transit photometry rejected by variability processing (variability_flag_bp_reject) (3) [NULL integer written as an empty string]

FIELD.name: VarRPr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: [0/1]? Average RP transit photometry rejected by variability processing (variability_flag_rp_reject) (3) [NULL integer written as an empty string]
